    <item>
      <title>about me</title>
      <link>https://fgiacomo.github.io/en/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://fgiacomo.github.io/en/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;prompt&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;~&lt;/span&gt; $ cat about.md&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;hero&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img class=&#34;avatar&#34; src=&#34;https://fgiacomo.github.io/foto.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Giacomo F.&#34;&#xA;         onerror=&#34;this.style.display=&#39;none&#39;;this.nextElementSibling.style.display=&#39;flex&#39;;&#34; /&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;avatar-placeholder&#34; style=&#34;display:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;üë§&lt;/span&gt;foto.jpg&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;hero-name&#34;&gt;Giacomo F.&lt;span class=&#34;cursor&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;hero-subtitle&#34;&gt;// Software Engineer ¬∑ Backend &amp;amp; Systems&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;hero-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span&gt;üìç Milan, Italy&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:tua@email.it&#34;&gt;tua@email.it&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/fgiacomo&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;github&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://linkedin.com/in/fgiacomo&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;linkedin&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;section class=&#34;section&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;section-title&#34;&gt;bio&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;body-text&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;Hey! I&#39;m a software engineer with 5+ years of experience building distributed systems and scalable APIs. I work mainly with Go and Python, and I spend more time than I&#39;d like to admit optimizing SQL queries.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;I started coding on my father&#39;s Commodore 64 and I&#39;ve been fascinated by making machines do things ever since. Professionally I&#39;ve specialized in backend work ‚Äî microservices, message queues, cloud infrastructure ‚Äî but the curiosity for &lt;em&gt;&#34;how does this actually work&#34;&lt;/em&gt; has never left me.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
