      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;prompt&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;~&lt;/span&gt; $ ls -la projects/&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;page-header&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;page-title&#34;&gt;projects&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;projects-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-top&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;project-name&#34;&gt;pgwatch-cli&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;project-links&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;project-link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/fgiacomo/pgwatch-cli&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;‚Üó github&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-desc&#34;&gt;Terminal tool to monitor slow queries and locks on PostgreSQL in real time. Supports JSON output, duration filters and webhook alerts.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag lang&#34;&gt;Go&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag lang&#34;&gt;PostgreSQL&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag&#34;&gt;CLI&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag done&#34;&gt;stable&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-top&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;project-name&#34;&gt;k8s-cost-estimator&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;project-links&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;project-link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/fgiacomo/k8s-cost&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;‚Üó github&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;project-link demo&#34; href=&#34;#&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;‚Üó demo&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-desc&#34;&gt;Kubectl plugin that estimates the monthly cost of pods on AWS/GCP/Azure based on requested resources and public VM pricing.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag lang&#34;&gt;Go&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag&#34;&gt;Kubernetes&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag&#34;&gt;AWS&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag done&#34;&gt;stable&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-top&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;project-name&#34;&gt;logpipe&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;project-links&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;project-link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/fgiacomo/logpipe&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;‚Üó github&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-desc&#34;&gt;Lightweight log aggregation pipeline for small teams who don&#39;t want to manage an ELK cluster. Supports regex, JSON parsing and S3 forwarding.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag lang&#34;&gt;Python&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag&#34;&gt;Kafka&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag&#34;&gt;S3&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag wip&#34;&gt;WIP&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-top&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;project-name&#34;&gt;this site&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;project-links&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;project-link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/fgiacomo/fgiacomo.github.io&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;‚Üó github&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-desc&#34;&gt;Bilingual personal site (IT/EN) with browser language auto-detection. Hugo with custom layout, terminal green aesthetic, deployed on GitHub Pages.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag lang&#34;&gt;HTML&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag lang&#34;&gt;CSS&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag&#34;&gt;GitHub Pages&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;p-tag done&#34;&gt;live&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
